        "text": "Hmm. The cron job has been working as planned, exit code 0, no unexpected output. The contents match between the Bugzilla output and the cached copy:\n```$ diff &lt;(curl -s $COOKIE \"<https:\/\/bugs.r-project.org\/buglist.cgi?chfieldfrom=7d&amp;ctype=atom&amp;title=Bugs%20changed%20in%20the%20last%207d>\") &lt;(curl -s <https:\/\/aitap.github.io\/Rbugs.atom\/7d.atom>) &amp;&amp; echo \"No changes\"\nNo changes```\nWhich of these updates were missing?\n```$ curl -s <https:\/\/aitap.github.io\/Rbugs.atom\/7d.atom> | grep '&lt;updated&gt;' | sort\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-03T11:09:19Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-03T15:29:22Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-03T16:24:37Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-04T10:55:39Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-05T00:34:12Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-07T00:00:43Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-08T04:22:42Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-09T20:31:20Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n    &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-09T21:31:44Z&lt;\/updated&gt;\n  &lt;updated&gt;2026-04-09T21:31:44Z&lt;\/updated&gt;```",
